@startuml m9-composite-liveness-signal-activity
skinparam dpi 300
title M9 — Composite Liveness vs TCP/HTTP Probe

start
:liveness probe fires;
:sample BEAM signals\n(scheduler util, run-queue,\nmailbox backpressure, restart intensity);
:compute composite progress score;
if (making real progress?) then (yes)
  #ccffcc:healthy;
  stop
else (no - wedged)
  #ccffcc:UNHEALTHY -> K8s restarts;
  stop
endif
legend right
  A naive TCP "port open" probe would
  falsely pass on a wedged VM (friction #1).
endlegend
@enduml
